title: Orangutan
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

"Old man of the Jungle", the orangutan is revered as a sentient being whom it is wrong to murder, he provides the model for the ape style ([[kalong|?]]) along with the rock ape. He teaches the techniques of invisibility, great strategic and intuitive awareness, deep strength, ‘long arm, short leg.’